{"lemma":"سُرْعانٌ","slug":"سُرْعانٌ","root":"س.ر.ع","root_slug":"س-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَرِيع","root":"سرع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19589","n19591"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fast (capable of moving with speed), quick (moving with speed)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sa.riːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19589","headword_ar":"سَرْعَانَ","root":"srE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroEaAna","text_ar":"سُرْعَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siroEaAna","text_ar":"سِرْعَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saruEaAna","text_ar":"سَرُعَانَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the last with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar,) occurring in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srEAna *aA xuruwjFA","text_ar":"سرعانَ ذَا خُرُوجًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, S, K,) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saruEa *aA xuruwjFA","text_ar":"سَرُعَ ذَا خُرُوجًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick is this in coming forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"how quick is this in coming forth!"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, which is nearly the same,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellently quick"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], (S, K,) are dial. vars., changed from the original form, which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saruEa","text_ar":"سَرُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and, for this reason, (S,) made indecl., with the final vowel of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saruEa","text_ar":"سَرُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for their termination. (S, K.) The word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srEAn","text_ar":"سرعان"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as a simple enunciative [placed before its inchoative], and also as an enunciative denoting wonder: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buToA=na","text_ar":"بُطْا=نَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and hence the saying, (K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lasaroEaAna maA","text_ar":"لَسَرْعَانَ مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEota ka*aA","text_ar":"صَنَعْتَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How quick was thy doing that!"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) The saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraEaAna *aA A_ihaAlapN","text_ar":"سَرَعَانَ ذَا اـِهَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"originated from the fact that a man had a lean ewe, her snivel running from her nostrils by reason of her leanness, and it being said to him “ What is this? ” he answered, “ Her grease: ” whereupon the asker said as above: the last word is in the accus. case as a denotative of state; and the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"how quick, is this"},{"kind":"text","text":"snivel [coming forth]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the state of melted grease!"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the last word is a specificative, under the supposition that the action is transferred [from its proper agent, which thus becomes a specificative], as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSab~aba zayodN EaraqFA","text_ar":"تَصَبَّبَ زَيْدٌ عَرَقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the meaning to be understood is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"how quick, is the melted grease of this!"},{"kind":"text","text":"the saying is applied to him who tells of a thing's coming to pass before its time: (O, K:) it is a prov. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroEaAnu","text_ar":"سَرْعَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and its fem.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroEaY","text_ar":"سَرْعَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariyEN","text_ar":"سَرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places: see also the paragraph here next following, in two places,"}],"source_refs":["S","K","IAar","O"]},{"entry_id":"n19591","headword_ar":"سَرُعَانَ","root":"srE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroEaAna","text_ar":"سَرْعَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}